dialogue_context.text: Hello Kimberly, Hope you're safe and doing well Thank you for writing an email to my colleague  Susan Thomas, about the PMP Certification Training . I' m Daniel Irwin, Learning Consultant at iCert Global and I will be your point of contact going forward. The PMP is the gold standard of project management certification. Recognized and demanded by organizations worldwide, the PMP validates your competence to perform in the role of a project manager, leading and directing projects and teams. In fact, the demand for project managers in the United States alone is projected to grow by up to 6.1 million jobs in less than two short years.
